ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 224, Prince Edward Island
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 224 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to the province of PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND, with respect to the Post-Tropical storm Dorian that occurred from September 7 to 8 2019.
